{ Hello chess fans! This is my 5th opening repertoire on one of my early childhood favorites: The Hyper-Accelerated Dragon. ❤️Please give this study a like and share with others! }
1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 g6 { The move order for the "Hyper-Accelerated Dragon". Although Black will often tranpose back to the more common Accelerated Dragon, this specific move order avoids the theoretical Rossolimo, which in my opinion scores well for the White side. } *


