1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 g6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nc6 5. Nc3 Bg7 6. Be3 Nf6 7. Bc4 O-O 8. Bb3 d6 9. f3 Na5 10. Qd2 Bd7 11. O-O-O Rb8 12. h4 b5 13. h5 Nc4 14. Bxc4 bxc4 15. hxg6 fxg6 16. Bh6 Qb6 17. b3 Bxh6 18. Qxh6 Rf7 { See game Batuhan Dastan - Nico Georgiadis below for a sample game in these kind of positions. Black's king usually is hard to crack. } *


